race.comment: RELEASE POINT (4) opened this prep with a couple of wins before failing in town last time when tested over 1900m. Back to a more suitable trip today so it will be no surprise to see him make amends. SHADOW DANE (14) missed the start and couldn't get involved at his latest run over 1300m at Dubbo. Fitter now and draws a decent gate for the first time this prep. Watch for a much better run. I'M SCARLETT (9) stormed home to win over this trip at Wellington two back. Struggled in open company last time but back in a BM66 she makes plenty of appeal. STAR INTRIGUE (12) dominated in front at Dubbo last start. Up in grade but should give backers a sight.
